Subclasses of IIRFilter in ddf.minim.effects

 class ChebFilter

 class HighPassSP

 class LowPassFS
          LowPassFS is a four stage low pass filter.

 class NotchFilter
          A notch filter removes a narrow band of frequencies from an audio signal.
